---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 180
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Obedience
By: St Vincent de Paul
---
A very powerful and efficacious medicament, and the means to purify
ourselves from every imperfection, to overcome all temptations and to
preserve in our heart imperturbable peace, is conformity to the will
of God.
